        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="S-9bwVPvVeq33lM2gUcA-59" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontStyle=1" value="MONITORAGGIO MANUALE" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="190" x="1810" y="950" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="APOLmTjzAg3qMuaqvKbE-1" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h3 data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;PROVA 2 - INSERIMENTO MONITORAGGIO MANUALE&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;1&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot; style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;Deve essere visualizzata la schermata iniziale &quot;PZ1&quot;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,1,0&quot;&gt;Cliccare sul tasto&amp;nbsp;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;2,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;19&quot;&gt;Monitoraggio Manuale&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;(tra le opzioni disponibili: Diario Clinico, Monitoraggio Manuale, Eventuali Note, Esci).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,2,0&quot;&gt;Il sistema apre la maschera di compilazione del sottoprocesso &quot;Monitoraggio Manuale&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,3,0&quot;&gt;Compilare il modulo &quot;Monitoraggio Manuale&quot; inserendo i dati richiesti.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,4,0&quot;&gt;Cliccare sul tasto&amp;nbsp;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;2,4,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;19&quot;&gt;CONFERMA&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,5,0&quot;&gt;Il sistema apre una finestra chiedendo conferma dell&#39;operazione.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,6,0&quot;&gt;Cliccare su&amp;nbsp;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;2,6,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;12&quot;&gt;Conferma&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;(all&#39;interno della finestra di dialogo).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,7,0&quot;&gt;Il sistema salva i dati e li invia alla cartella specialistica.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,8,0&quot;&gt;Il sistema visualizza l&#39;esito e attende che l&#39;utente clicchi su &#39;OK&#39;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,9,0&quot;&gt;Cliccare su&amp;nbsp;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;2,9,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;12&quot;&gt;OK&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,10,0&quot;&gt;Il sistema chiude la maschera del monitoraggio e ritorna automaticamente alla schermata iniziale &quot;PZ1&quot; .&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,11,0&quot;&gt;Verificare che nella cartella specialistica i dati di monitoraggio siano stati memorizzati correttamente.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="485" width="390" x="2690" y="1137.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="APOLmTjzAg3qMuaqvKbE-2" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontStyle=0" value="&lt;h3 data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot;&gt;PROVA 3 - CHIUSURA APP&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;1&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot; style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,0,0&quot;&gt;Deve essere visualizzata la schermata iniziale &quot;PZ1&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,1,0&quot;&gt;Cliccare sul tasto&amp;nbsp;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;4,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;19&quot;&gt;Esci&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;(tra le opzioni disponibili: Diario Clinico, Monitoraggio Manuale, Eventuali Note, Esci).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,2,0&quot;&gt;Il sistema apre una window (finestra di dialogo) chiedendo conferma dell&#39;operazione.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,3,0&quot;&gt;Cliccare su&amp;nbsp;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;4,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;12&quot;&gt;Conferma&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;(all&#39;interno della finestra di dialogo).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,4,0&quot;&gt;Il sistema esegue l&#39;operazione &quot;Chiusura applicazione&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,5,0&quot;&gt;Verificare che l&#39;applicazione sia terminata correttamente e che la finestra sia chiusa.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="485" width="390" x="3680" y="1045" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
